snippet.title: Senua's Saga: Hellblade II - Gameplay reveal
snippet.description: Debuted at The Game Awards 2021, watch the Senua’s Saga: Hellblade II gameplay reveal. Coming exclusively to Xbox and Windows PC from Ninja Theory. Captured in-game by the development team.
